====================
Standards
====================

All Solar classes follow a common set of implementation standards.

* They each adhere to a common [[StyleGuide]] of coding standards

* They use a standard set of [[NamingConventions]]

* Each descends from a common lightweight [[BaseClass]]

* They all use the same [[ConstructorParameters]] for instantiation

* Each reads its configuration from a common [[ConfigFile]]

* All are ready for localization using their own set of [[LocaleFiles]]
